<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>٥٠٩ - حَدَّثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1660">‌حُمَيْدُ بْنُ مَسْعَدَةَ، </a>ثَنَا <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">‌إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/1760">‌خَالِدٍ الْحَذَّاءِ، </a>عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/3667">‌أَبِي قِلَابَةَ </a>، عَنْ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/822">‌أَنَسٍ </a>مِثْلَ حَدِيثِ وُهَيْبٍ، قَالَ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/634">‌إِسْمَاعِيلُ </a>: فَحَدَّثْتُ بِهِ <a href="https://shamela.ws/narrator/857">‌أَيُّوبَ </a>فَقَالَ: <span class="c2">«إِلَّا الْإِقَامَةَ»</span>.<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p> </div>